column8: Capacity Request in Velocity is a workflow designed to enable researchers to request space for experimental or seed production workflows in Open Fields, Controlled Environments, and Labs across Bayer's Crop Science business units. It offers various functionalities, including creating new requests, saving requests in draft mode, and checking the status of existing requests. It stores information for all the capacity requests.
